languages.text: {n}Мужчина со слезами счастья смотрит то на вас, то на свою ладонь.{/n} "Храни вас Император!"
{n}He stares at you, then at his hand, then at you again, his eyes filling with tears of joy.{/n} "Emperor keep you!"

languages.text: {n}Er starrt zuerst dich, dann seine Hand und schließlich erneut dich an. In seinen Augen erkennst du Freudentränen.{/n} "Der Imperator sei mit Euch!"
languages.original_text: {n}He stares at you, then at his hand, then at you again, his eyes filling with tears of joy.{/n} "Emperor keep you!"

languages.text: {n}Son regard tombe sur vous, puis sur sa main, avant de revenir sur vous, les yeux pleins de larmes de joie.{/n} « Que l'Empereur veille sur vous ! »
languages.original_text: {n}He stares at you, then at his hand, then at you again, his eyes filling with tears of joy.{/n} "Emperor keep you!"

traits.locale_text: {n}Son regard tombe sur vous, puis sur sa main, avant de revenir sur vous, les yeux pleins de larmes de joie.{/n} « Que l'Empereur veille sur vous ! »

languages.text: {n}Te mira fijamente, se mira la mano y vuelve a mirarte, llorando de alegría.{/n} «¡Que el Emperador le proteja!».

languages.text: {n}彼は、あなたを見つめてから、自分の手を見て、そして再びあなたを見た。彼の目は喜びの涙でいっぱいだ。{/n}「皇帝があなたをお守りくださるでしょう！」
languages.original_text: {n}He stares at you, then at his hand, then at you again, his eyes filling with tears of joy.{/n} "Emperor keep you!"

languages.text: {n}他盯着你，之后盯着自己的手，之后再次盯着你，双眼充满了喜悦的泪水。{/n}“愿帝皇保佑您！”

languages.text: {n}Bir sana, bir eline sonra tekrar sana bakıyor. Ardından gözleri mutluluktan yaşarıyor.{/n} "İmparator sizi korusun!"
